high_descs: Look down, then turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the mug and spoon that is to the left of the sink.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk back over to the sink.
Place the mug and spoon into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in the sink basin.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the sink on the left.
Pick up the mug with spoon next to the sink.
Bring the mug with spoon to the sink to the right.
Put the mug with spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with spoon in the sink.

high_descs: turn around to the sink
grab the bowl and the spoon by the sink
walk to the left a little
put the bowl and the spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: move the bowl with the spoon from by the sink into the sink

high_descs: Turn around and then turn left so you are facing the sink
Pick up a cup with the spoon attached
Move to your left, and then face the kitchen sink from the opposite angle as before
Place the cup and spoon into the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a cup and spoon into the sink

high_descs: turn around, walk forward, turn left to face sink
pick up the mug with spoon that is by the sink
take a few steps to the right
put the mug with spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: move a mug with spoon in to the sink
